{"_id":"1f0616ec-2971-4c0b-b7f3-72d5ea715920","type":"ability","name":"Rune Forger","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Rune Forger","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You are able to learn to scribe a single rank 1 Arcana rune of your choice.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"25edd901-1d79-40b8-a215-e8d491100ba6","type":"ability","name":"Propaganda","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Propaganda","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"Given an hour you can craft flyers, an article, a rousing speech, or similar written work to turn public opinion to your side or to spread a rumour. If you write a speech, you help the reader using your Scribe skill, or use your Scribe skill if you perform it yourself. If you spread other propaganda, the benefit is up to you and the GM, but will generally either result in a Boon on social interactions with affected individuals or the removal of a Consequence from the tracker, as appropriate.","roll_type":"","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"307d19db-ade0-4998-86b5-e75094dac713","type":"skill","name":"Scribe","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill_id":"scribe","domain":"Technology and Sciences","rank":1,"stat":"intelligence","description":"Beyond creating, forging, and identifying documents, the Scribe skill is used to navigate buerocracy, permits, and laws."}}
{"_id":"4a9da561-8f19-40ff-866d-0dc252deaba5","type":"ability","name":"Forger","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Forger","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intelligence","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You can create convincing false documents such as permits, identification, orders, ledgers, or correspondence. You only roll to determine how convincing they are when you present them to another person, and make a new check for each person they are presented to. Creating them takes 10 minutes to an hour, depending on the complexity.","roll_type":"","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"4b417e20-0b52-429a-b2e3-ff1d32d3077a","type":"ability","name":"Red Tape","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Red Tape","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"Your knowledge of burocracy is such that you can tie others up in red tape --- or cut through it. You gain a Boon on all checks related to navigating burocracy. You may use your Scribe skill --- with this Boon applied --- any time you attempt to sway someone using burocracy or the law, whether you are being truthful or not (for example, by citing obscure legal codes to convince the City Watch not to arrest you).","roll_type":"","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"5cd3a1a0-a587-40c9-95e5-76a05932cb23","type":"ability","name":"Linguist","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Linguist","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You learn a language of your choice. You may choose this ability multiple times, each time you gain a different language.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"6d188f9b-cb0c-4011-bedf-ae70ef7d2da5","type":"ability","name":"Codebreaker","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Codebreaker","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You gain a Boon on all checks related to breaking, noticing, or intercepting secret messages, to noticing forgeries, and to identifying the origin of messages or text based on things like penmanship or writing styles.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"8586d28c-d1b7-4516-ac42-d48d7720f6b9","type":"ability","name":"Legaleze","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Legaleze","rank":"3","type":"technique","action":"slow","defense":"intelligence","target":"Single","range":"Short","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You confound the target with legaleze, causing Heavy Intelligence damage. This cannot inflict Wounds. This is not considered a hostile action when used out of combat, though upon a failure the target realizes what you are doing and may react poorly to it.","roll_type":"","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"89ca4d63-c60a-475f-bbc0-f32531705f37","type":"ability","name":"Encyclopedic","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Encyclopedic","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You are very widely read. You may use this to grant yourself a Boon to a check made to recall knowledge you may conceivably have read about before.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"a892dc87-56ea-45c3-af41-1f6845f28831","type":"ability","name":"Propaganda Network","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Propaganda Network","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You are a member of or have access to an entire propaganda network. You choose the nature of this network when taking this ability --- it could be a news organization, an organization that makes seditious anticapitalist pamphlets, or even a high society gossip mill. You may call on them to assist you in Ventures at times (at the GM's discretion). When you begin a Venture in a region where they operate, your group begins with 1 less Consequence.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"b142f50b-8207-4b11-85eb-856ae7255f50","type":"ability","name":"Paper Trail","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Paper Trail","rank":"3","type":"activity","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You can track known individuals through the traces they leave in public records, reconstructing their movements and history. By spending an hour with access to public records, you gain a Boon on all checks made regarding a person of your choice. You may also ask the GM broad questions (who are this person's connections, is this official corrupt, what business incentives does this person have) and get an answer.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"da2c1b9e-f076-45fa-9052-662dcc185d28","type":"ability","name":"Cartography","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Cartography","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"As long as you have maps of the area, you can use Scribe to navigate.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"scribe"}}
{"_id":"deaece3d-b208-4d0d-9a9d-711870142d2a","type":"ability","name":"Legal Loophole","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/scribe.svg","system":{"skill":"Scribe","name":"Legal Loophole","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"3","description":"Once per Venture, you may use this ability to overcome a legal or burocratic obstacle, within reason, without rolling a check.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"scribe"}}
